name: Space Trucker Poutine Inc
description:
A little arcade scroller game built in 14 hours for the first JabeJam ever!

The selected themes were : Poutine(the food), Trucks and Mars
So I went with a Poutine delivery truck chilling on the red planet!!

Dodge the obstacles, grab powerups and make sure you don't end up with no fuel to fight for the highscore!!

#arcade #other #JabeJam1
